quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,41,"Ndi iwo amene adasamuka ndi cholinga chokondweretsa Mulungu pambuyo poponderezedwa, Ife, ndithudi, tidzawakhazika padziko mwamtendere. Koma malipiro a tsiku lachiweruzo adzakhala aakulu kwambiri iwo akadadziwa"
  16,42,Iwo amene adapirira ndipo adaika chikhulupiriro mwa Ambuye wawo
  16,43,"Iwe usanadze Ife sitidatumizepo, ena koma amuna amene tidawapatsa chivumbulutso chathu. Kotero afunse iwo odziwa mawu a Mulungu ngati iwe siukudziwa"
  16,44,"Ndi zizindikiro zooneka ndiponso mabuku opatulika, Ife tavumbulutsa kwa iwe chikumbutso kuti ulalikire anthu zonse zimene zatumizidwa kwa iwo ndi kuti akhoza kulingirira"
  16,45,Kodi iwo amene amakonza chiwembu ndi odzikhulupirira kuti Mulungu sangawakwirire m’nthaka kapena kuti chilango sichingagwe pa iwo kuchokera ku mbali imene sali kuiyembekezera
  16,46,Kapena iwo ali ndi chikhulupiriro chakuti Iye sadzawagwira iwo m’maulendo awo pamene sangathe kuthawa
  16,47,Kapena kuti Iye sangawapatse chionongeko cha pang’onopang’ono? Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye Mwini chifundo ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  16,48,"Kodi iwo sakuziona zinthu zimene Mulungu adalenga mmene zimagwetsera mithunzi yake kumbali ya dzanja lamanja ndi ku dzanja lamanzere, kumulambira Mulungu modzichepetsa"
  16,49,"Ndipo kwa Mulungu zimagwada zinthu zonse za mlengalenga ndi za padziko lapansi ndi zonse za moyo ndi angelo, ndipo sizidzikweza"
  16,50,Izo zimaopa Ambuye wawo amene ali pamwamba pawo ndipo zimachita monga momwe zalamulidwira